			<div class="content" id="post-content-4799208">
									

<p>This is technically my second 001 proposal, but it's my first one on the EN wiki. Still a -J though, so some folks still might say it doesn't count. Guess this means I need to work on my <em>serious</em> 001 proposal.</p>
