														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4799319">
									

<p>I don't particularly like this - it feels like a version of swann's proposal just without any subtlety. There's little here beyond &quot;what if the roleplayers had a point&quot; and it's such a basic premise that anyone who frequents chat could come up with if they base their ideation process on the things they see around then, which is a method I've always spoken out against.</p>
<p>But you had me at &quot;We've been using the Wikidot domain for years!&quot;, and my vote for -Js is based on whether or not I laughed, so it's a +1 from me.</p>

